[30;1m105 | [0m[35mThe middleware is intended to be used inline with OpenStack WSGI components,[0m
[30;1m106 | [0m[35mbased on the Oslo WSGI middleware class. It is typically deployed[0m
[30;1m107 | [0m[35mas a configuration element in a paste configuration pipeline of other[0m
[30;1m108 | [0m[35mmiddleware components, with the pipeline terminating in the service[0m
[30;1m109 | [0m[35mapplication. The middleware conforms to the python WSGI standard [PEP-333]_.[0m
[30;1m110 | [0m[35mIn initializing the middleware, a configuration item (which acts like a python[0m
[30;1m111 | [0m[35mdictionary) is passed to the middleware with relevant configuration options.[0m
